data.description: Fresh paint throughout, less than a year old, this 4-bed, 2.5-bath gem in Richmond Hill is ready for its new owner! The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless appliances and a huge island overlooking the dining area and great room. The spacious owner’s suite features an enormous walk-in closet, raised height vanities & a 5-foot fiberglass shower. The house sits on a premium lot with privacy fence. Tons of storage space throughout. Abundant natural light creates the perfect blend of style and comfort. Enjoy amenities such as the community pool and playground. This house also has the ideal location, half a mile away from Frances Meeks Elementary and Richmond Hill Middle School and less than a mile from the construction site of the new high school and nearly 5 miles to the interstate. Don't miss out, schedule your private tour today!
